observations.recommendation:
We recommended that the Municipal Mayor:
provide the necessary support in enjoining the remaining barangays to establish their own MRF;
seek an ordinance from the Sangguniang Bayan to strictly implement waste segregation at source and the no segregation/no collection rule;
designate a personnel to supervise the operation in the open dumpsite; and
provide additional budget to develop and operate a fully functional sanitary landfill including machineries and equipment, as a final disposal site for solid and, eventually, residual wastes of the municipality after the safe closure of the current open dumpsite.
